poverty, kahirapan, kakabos.tweet_text:
Senators, congress reps & cabinet members got a pay hike 7 times the P10,481 poverty line this year — their monthly salaries increased by P71,601 to P295,191.

Pres. Duterte’s was 10 times the poverty line — increasing by P101,656 to P399,739.

So, yay, PH poverty is going down.
